import React from 'react'
import ReactDom from 'react-dom/client'
import { BrowserRouter as Routers, Route, Routes,Link } from 'react-router-dom'

import Personalized_data_Part from './0_component/Personalized_data_TabNevBar/Personalized_data_Part'
import Personalized_data_progresser from './0_component/Personalized_data_TabNevBar/Personalized_data_progresser'

const root = ReactDom.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'))

root.render(
    <React.Fragment>
            
           

<Routers>
    <Routes>
        <Route path='/' element={<Personalized_data_progresser/>}></Route>
        <Route path='/home' element={<Personalized_data_progresser/>}></Route>
    </Routes>

    
</Routers>
<Link></Link>

      <Personalized_data_Part/>

    </React.Fragment>
)
